subNode:value.scalar:string: Activate or deactivate your shop (It is a good idea to deactivate your shop while you perform maintenance. Please note that the webservice will not be disabled).
IP addresses allowed to access the Front Office even if the shop is disabled. Please use a comma to separate them (e.g. 42.24.4.2,127.0.0.1,99.98.97.96)
